<MuClidPreset presetName="A8_tail" presetDescription="Tail-out test A8: a long-decay tonal synth hit on every beat (free-running). Swapping to the empty TS2 mid-play retires the running voice, which must ring out smoothly across the loop-point commit and decay over ~1s rather than hard-cutting. Deeper than TS_swap (which uses a short kick): asserts the tail is present right after the commit AND decays AND reaches silence." presetCategory="test">
